item.title: CVE-2021-34657|2024-09-16T16:42:55.151Z -- typofr -- typofr
item.description: The 2TypoFR WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the text function found in the ~/vendor/Org_Heigl/Hyphenator/index.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 0.11.
